         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757"><!-- p3l5-r8 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Hd1e108">Rubrica 8</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De tacendis et celandis propriis et alienis criminibus</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>
      ¶ De tacendis et celandis propriis
      <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>et alienis criminibus. Rubrica. 8.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="64"/> <ref>SAlomon in prouerbi. c.
      <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>11.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e127">Qui ambu
        <lb ed="#V" n="66" break="no"/>lat fraudulenter reuelat archana.
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>qui autem fidelis est celat amici com
        <lb ed="#V" n="68" break="no"/>missa.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e137"> 
             / <ref>20. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e139">Si qui reuelat mysteria et am
        <lb ed="#V" n="69" break="no"/>bulat fraudulentur et dilatat anima sua ne com
        <lb ed="#V" n="70" break="no"/>miscearis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e148"> 
             / <ref>25. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e150">Secretum extraneo ne re
        <lb ed="#V" n="71" break="no"/>ueles.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e156"> 
             / <ref>31. c. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e158">Nullum secretum est vbi
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>regnat ebrietas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e164">
               <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>¶ <ref>Micheas propheta. c. 7. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e168">Ab ea que dor
        <lb ed="#V" n="74" break="no"/>mit in sinu tuo custodi claustra oris tui.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e174">
               <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>¶ <ref>Socrates: in exhortationibus. c. 2.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e178">Serua mage verborum quam rerum deposita.
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>De ineffabilibus nulli dicas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e186">
               <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>¶ <ref>Iesus filius sirach: in ecclesiast. c. 27.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e190">Qui
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>denudat archana amici fidem perdit: et non
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>inueniet amicum ad animum suum. Denudare ami
        <lb ed="#V" n="81" break="no"/>ci mysteria desperatio est animae infelicis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e200">
               <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e204">¶ <ref>Oratius: in epistolis. 5. c.</ref> Que non ebrietas
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>designat operta recludit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e211">
               <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>/ <ref>Idem in sermonibus l. serm. 4.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e215">Qui non iussa potest commissa tacere.
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>Qui nequit. hic miser est. hunc tu romane
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>caueto.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e225"> 
             / <ref>Li. 2 serm. 8. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e227">Res
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>Aduerse nudare solent: celare secunde.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e233">
               <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>¶ <ref>Ouidius sine titulo: seu amorum. li. 2. c. 2.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e237">Conscius assiduos commissi tollet honores <!--192.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="77-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>Quis minor est autem quam tacuisse labor</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e251">
               <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>/ <ref>Idem de arte amandi. li. 2.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>  <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e255">Eximia est virtus prestare silentia rebus
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>At contra grauis est culpa tacenda loqui.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e263">
               <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>¶ <ref>Quintilianus declam. 17. et fi. declam.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>  <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e267">Obserua sermones: secreta custodi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e273">
               <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>¶ <ref>Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum. li. 8. c. 1. et p.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>  <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e277">Hos mores habem populos: hos imperitissimus
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>quisque in secreta irrumpere cupit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e286"> 
             / <ref>Li. 18. c.
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e288">Habet vnusquisque aliquem cui tantum cre
        <lb ed="#V" n="11" break="no"/>dat quantum ipsi creditum est: vt garrulitatem
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>suam custodiat: et contentus sic vnius auribus po
        <lb ed="#V" n="13" break="no"/>pulum faciat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e300"> 
             / <ref>Idem de moribus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e302">Quod taci
        <lb ed="#V" n="14" break="no"/>tum esse velis nemini dixeris. Sed tibiipsi non
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>imperasti: quomodo ab alio filentium speras: Quid
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>dulcius quam habere amicum cum quo omnia sicut
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>tecum audeas loqui.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e314"> 
             / <ref>Idem tragediarum in
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/><sic>hypolto.</sic> 9. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e316">Alium filere quod voles prius sile.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e322">
               <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>¶ <ref>Uegetius: de re militari. li. 3. t. 36 et fina.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e326">Nulla consilia sunt meliora quam illa que
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>ignorauerint aduersarius tuus antequam facias.
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>Cum consilium tuum cognouerit aduersarius pro
        <lb ed="#V" n="23" break="no"/>ditum dispositionem mutare te conuenit.
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>Quid fieri debeat tractato cum multis. Quod
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>vero facturus sis cum paucissimus: vel potius
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>ipse tecum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e345">
               <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>¶ <ref>Cato. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e349">Consilium archanum tacito com
        <lb ed="#V" n="28" break="no"/>mitte fideli.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e355">
               <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>¶ <ref>Isydorus soliloquiorum. li. 2. c. 43.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e359">Commu
        <lb ed="#V" n="30" break="no"/>nia omnibus secreta perfectioribus loquere.
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>Apta cunctis: operta paucis denuncia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e368">
               <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>¶ <ref>Mattheus vindocinensis in poetria. partis
        <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>2. et fi. c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e372">Lingua loquax reticenda refert
        <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>elimina edit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e380">
               <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>¶ <ref>Andreas ad gualterium de amore. lib. 3</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="36"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e384">Secretum tuum ab omni femina custodi
        <lb ed="#V" n="37" break="no"/>re stude.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-d1e392">
               <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>¶ <ref>Iacobus beneuentanus. c. 42.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62757-Qd1e396">Si secretum
        <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>fui cordis tibi pandit amicus:
        <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>Uxori fili ne reserato tue.
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>Non bene secretum mulier tenet: immo reuelat.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
